extendedInfo.description: Thank you for your interest in the Keen Group Minicabs and Couriers Android App. This App allows you to book a Private Hire vehicle from the Keen Group. You can:  Get a Quotation for your journey  Make a booking  Check its status  Cancel a booking  Track the vehicle on a map  Manage your previous bookings  Manage your favourite addresses The App is intended for U.K. use only, and therefore all addresses are restricted to within the U.K.

reviews.title: Stick with Hailo - Black Cabs!
reviews.comment: This company and its service is rubbish! Why take second best with a sat nav when you can get a black cab for less with a driver that has a map in his/her head. Hailo is \302\2435 minimum too...
reviews.author: English Capricorn
